Homeland Insecurity II

In "Johnny Saturn: Homeland Insecurity" part II, Dr. Wissenschaft is quickly dying, but not before he fulfills his contract with the Star Cabal to harness the living essence of oppression and fear and turn it loose on Spire City! But questions remain: whose agenda is Dr. Wissenschaft really following? Also in this issue, when a hero runs from danger and abandons his teammates, how does it affect his psyche?
